---
// Our Story section + Key Facts panel
import SectionHeader from '../SectionHeader.astro';
---
<section class="relative py-24 sm:py-32 lg:py-40 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] ambient-blob bg-gold-400"></div>

  <div class="section-inner max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 relative z-10">
    <SectionHeader label="Our Story" labelHy="&#1348;&#1381;&#1408; &#1354;&#1377;&#1407;&#1396;&#1400;&#1410;&#1385;&#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1398;&#1384;" />

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 mt-12">
      <div class="gs-reveal">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-text-primary font-semibold mb-8 leading-[1.15]">
          <span data-i18n
            data-hy="&#1344;&#1387;&#1396;&#1398;&#1406;&#1377;&#1390; &#1392;&#1377;&#1397;&#1391;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; &#1393;&#1381;&#1404;&#1398;&#1381;&#1408;&#1391;&#1377;&#1407;&#1400;&#1410;&#1385;&#1397;&#1377;&#1398; &#1392;&#1377;&#1382;&#1377;&#1408;&#1377;&#1396;&#1397;&#1377; &#1377;&#1406;&#1377;&#1398;&#1380;&#1400;&#1410;&#1397;&#1385;&#1398;&#1381;&#1408;&#1387; &#1406;&#1408;&#1377;"
            data-en="Founded on the Traditions of Armenian Entrepreneurship">
            Founded on the Traditions of Armenian Entrepreneurship
          </span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-[16px] text-card-body font-light leading-[1.8]">
          <p data-i18n
             data-hy="&#1344;&#1377;&#1397;&#1381;&#1408;&#1384; &#1380;&#1377;&#1408;&#1381;&#1408;&#1387; &#1384;&#1398;&#1385;&#1377;&#1409;&#1412;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396; &#1381;&#1394;&#1381;&#1388; &#1381;&#1398; &#1377;&#1399;&#1389;&#1377;&#1408;&#1392;&#1387; &#1377;&#1404;&#1415;&#1407;&#1408;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398;&#1398;&#1381;&#1408;&#1417;"
             data-en="Armenia has been a crossroads of trade for millennia. From the ancient Silk Road merchants to the modern-day global diaspora &mdash; Armenians have always understood the art of creating value across borders. Algosphere Asset Management was founded to carry this legacy forward into the world of institutional asset management.">
            Armenia has been a crossroads of trade for millennia. From the ancient Silk Road merchants to the modern-day global diaspora &mdash; Armenians have always understood the art of creating value across borders. Algosphere Asset Management was founded to carry this legacy forward into the world of institutional asset management.
          </p>
          <p data-i18n
             data-hy="&#1348;&#1381;&#1408; &#1377;&#1398;&#1400;&#1410;&#1398;&#1384;&#1373; &laquo;Algosphere&raquo;&#1373; &#1396;&#1387;&#1377;&#1406;&#1400;&#1408;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396; &#1383; &#1377;&#1388;&#1379;&#1400;&#1408;&#1387;&#1385;&#1396;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; &#1396;&#1400;&#1407;&#1381;&#1409;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396;&#1384; &#1415; &#1392;&#1377;&#1396;&#1377;&#1385;&#1387;&#1406; &#1407;&#1381;&#1405;&#1388;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398;&#1417;"
             data-en="Our name &mdash; Algosphere &mdash; unites &lsquo;algorithmic&rsquo; thinking with a &lsquo;sphere&rsquo; of influence. It encapsulates our belief that the best investment outcomes emerge when rigorous quantitative analysis meets nuanced human judgment and deep local market knowledge.">
            Our name &mdash; Algosphere &mdash; unites &lsquo;algorithmic&rsquo; thinking with a &lsquo;sphere&rsquo; of influence. It encapsulates our belief that the best investment outcomes emerge when rigorous quantitative analysis meets nuanced human judgment and deep local market knowledge.
          </p>
          <p data-i18n
             data-hy="&#1329;&#1397;&#1405;&#1413;&#1408; &#1344;&#1377;&#1397;&#1377;&#1405;&#1407;&#1377;&#1398;&#1384; &#1382;&#1378;&#1377;&#1394;&#1381;&#1409;&#1398;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396; &#1383; &#1407;&#1398;&#1407;&#1381;&#1405;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; &#1406;&#1381;&#1408;&#1377;&#1411;&#1400;&#1389;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396;&#1417; &#1329;&#1404;&#1377;&#1403;&#1387;&#1398; &#1407;&#1381;&#1389;&#1398;&#1400;&#1388;&#1400;&#1379;&#1387;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; &#1392;&#1377;&#1396;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1408;&#1379;&#1384; &#1415; &#1405;&#1411;&#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1404;&#1412;&#1387; &#1398;&#1381;&#1408;&#1400;&#1410;&#1386;&#1384; &#1344;&#1377;&#1397;&#1377;&#1405;&#1407;&#1377;&#1398;&#1387;&#1398; &#1380;&#1377;&#1408;&#1393;&#1398;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396; &#1381;&#1398; &#1381;&#1382;&#1377;&#1391;&#1387; &#1398;&#1381;&#1408;&#1380;&#1408;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396;&#1377;&#1397;&#1387;&#1398; &#1400;&#1410;&#1394;&#1394;&#1400;&#1410;&#1385;&#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1398;&#1417;"
             data-en="Today, Armenia is experiencing an extraordinary economic transformation. With a $2.6 billion technology sector, 200+ fintech companies, and a diaspora of 7&ndash;10 million, the country sits at the intersection of ancient heritage and modern innovation &mdash; creating a unique investment destination that Algosphere was built to serve.">
            Today, Armenia is experiencing an extraordinary economic transformation. With a $2.6 billion technology sector, 200+ fintech companies, and a diaspora of 7&ndash;10 million, the country sits at the intersection of ancient heritage and modern innovation &mdash; creating a unique investment destination that Algosphere was built to serve.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="gs-reveal-right">
        <!-- Key facts panel -->
        <div class="glass-card p-10 lg:p-12">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-card-title font-semibold mb-8" data-i18n data-hy="&#1344;&#1387;&#1396;&#1398;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; &#1359;&#1406;&#1397;&#1377;&#1388;&#1398;&#1381;&#1408;" data-en="Key Facts">Key Facts</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 border border-glass-border rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-gold-400/[0.03] shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8.25M15.75 21v-8.25M8.25 21v-8.25M3 9l9-6 9 6m-1.5 12V10.332A48.36 48.36 0 0012 9.75c-2.551 0-5.056.2-7.5.582V21M3 21h18M12 6.75h.008v.008H12V6.75z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-text-primary text-[15px] font-medium" data-i18n data-hy="&#1344;&#1387;&#1396;&#1398;&#1377;&#1380;&#1408;&#1406;&#1377;&#1390;" data-en="Established">Established</p>
                <p class="text-card-body-muted text-[14px] font-light mt-1">2024 &middot; Yerevan, Armenia</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 border border-glass-border rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-gold-400/[0.03] shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-text-primary text-[15px] font-medium" data-i18n data-hy="&#1343;&#1377;&#1408;&#1379;&#1377;&#1406;&#1400;&#1408;&#1396;&#1377;&#1398; &#1343;&#1377;&#1408;&#1379;&#1377;&#1406;&#1387;&#1395;&#1377;&#1391;" data-en="Regulatory Status">Regulatory Status</p>
                <p class="text-card-body-muted text-[14px] font-light mt-1" data-i18n
                   data-hy="&#1340;&#1387;&#1409;&#1381;&#1398;&#1382;&#1377;&#1406;&#1400;&#1408;&#1406;&#1377;&#1390; &#1344;&#1377;&#1397;&#1377;&#1405;&#1407;&#1377;&#1398;&#1387; &#1343;&#1381;&#1398;&#1407;&#1408;&#1400;&#1398;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; &#1330;&#1377;&#1398;&#1391;&#1387; &#1391;&#1400;&#1394;&#1396;&#1387;&#1409;"
                   data-en="Licensed by the Central Bank of Armenia">Licensed by the Central Bank of Armenia</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 border border-glass-border rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-gold-400/[0.03] shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-text-primary text-[15px] font-medium" data-i18n data-hy="&#1366;&#1400;&#1398;&#1380;&#1387; &#1359;&#1381;&#1405;&#1377;&#1391;" data-en="Fund Type">Fund Type</p>
                <p class="text-card-body-muted text-[14px] font-light mt-1" data-i18n
                   data-hy="&#1363;&#1377;&#1391;, &#1400;&#1401; &#1392;&#1408;&#1377;&#1402;&#1377;&#1408;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1397;&#1387;&#1398; &#1398;&#1381;&#1408;&#1380;&#1408;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396;&#1377;&#1397;&#1387;&#1398; &#1411;&#1400;&#1398;&#1380;&#1381;&#1408;"
                   data-en="Closed-end, non-public investment funds">Closed-end, non-public investment funds</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 border border-glass-border rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-gold-400/[0.03] shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-text-primary text-[15px] font-medium" data-i18n data-hy="&#1331;&#1408;&#1377;&#1405;&#1381;&#1398;&#1397;&#1377;&#1391;" data-en="Headquarters">Headquarters</p>
                <p class="text-card-body-muted text-[14px] font-light mt-1">Argishtii 7/6, Yerevan 0015</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 border border-glass-border rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-gold-400/[0.03] shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-text-primary text-[15px] font-medium" data-i18n data-hy="&#1337;&#1387;&#1408;&#1377;&#1397;&#1387;&#1398; &#1350;&#1381;&#1408;&#1380;&#1408;&#1400;&#1394;&#1398;&#1381;&#1408;" data-en="Target Investors">Target Investors</p>
                <p class="text-card-body-muted text-[14px] font-light mt-1" data-i18n
                   data-hy="&#1352;&#1408;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1406;&#1400;&#1408;&#1406;&#1377;&#1390; &#1398;&#1381;&#1408;&#1380;&#1408;&#1400;&#1394;&#1398;&#1381;&#1408; &#1415; &#1405;&#1411;&#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1404;&#1412;&#1387; &#1398;&#1381;&#1408;&#1391;&#1377;&#1397;&#1377;&#1409;&#1400;&#1410;&#1409;&#1387;&#1401;&#1398;&#1381;&#1408;"
                   data-en="Qualified investors &amp; Armenian diaspora">Qualified investors &amp; Armenian diaspora</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
